data.title: Ethereum price prediction: Tom Lee targets $7,000–$9,000 and explains why ETH could outperform Bitcoin (BTC USD) by next year
data.description: Ethereum price prediction 2026: Tom Lee forecasts Ethereum's price could dip to $2,500 before skyrocketing to $7,000–$9,000. He emphasizes Ethereum's strong developer base and institutional interest as key factors for its future performance.
data.keywords: Ethereum price prediction, Tom Lee Ethereum forecast, cryptocurrency market analysis, Bitcoin vs Ethereum, Ethereum price surge
